                        img(src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/bannertitleImg1_325_100.png", alt="")
                    p The white horse baby is a warm, dreamy urban forest dreamer. In his world, it is a castle that can dream of the wind. It is awonderland.
            section.overview
                h6 overview
                ul
                    li
                        p About story
                            span.bgColor
                    li
                        p Series products
                            span.bgColor
        article.introduction
            section._img
                figure
                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/intrImg_260_240.png", alt="")
            section._title
                h6 introduction
                h5 About story
                    span.bgColor
                p From the dreamy "Happy Forest" white horse baby, the biggest magic is to bring you happiness, laughter, let you forget the pressure and trouble! <br/><br/>We have cooperated with the forest-based writer "Beiguo Teacher" who has always been concentric, caring and warm-hearted to create a "white horse baby". The white horse baby is a warm, dreamy urban forest dreamer. In his world, it is a castle that can dream of the wind. It is a wonderful wonderland.
        article.product 
            section._title
                h6 OVERVIEW
                h5 Series products
                    span.bgColor
            section.productContent
                ul
                    each val in product
                        //後端請注意: 下方data-src請放置燈箱資料位置
                        li(data-src="../whitehorsebaby/detail.html" class=(val.newOne=="true")?"new":"")
                            ._img
                                figure
                                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src=val.img, alt="")
                                .hoverBox
                                    span
                                .newOne
                                    p NEW
                            ._text
                                p.name=val.name
                                p.words=val.words
                                .price
                                    p=val.price
                                    span=val.ps
                                
            section.buttons
                figure.right
                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/buttonsRightImg2_180_300.png", alt="")
                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/buttonsRightImg1_220_300.png", alt="")
                h6 For pre-order, please contact the businessoffices in each district.
                div
                    a.leanbutton(href="javascript:void")
                        p Showroom
                    a.leanbutton(href="javascript:void")
                        p Online shop
                figure.left
                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/buttonsLeftImg1_300_200.png", alt="")
                    img.b-lazy(src=blazy data-src="../../upload/fa2/whitehorsebaby/buttonsLeftImg2_200_200.png", alt="")
